claim.claim-text:
1. A replaceable module for a notebook computer with an insert slot concavely disposed on the surface of an external housing body of a display apparatus of the said notebook computer comprises of: 
a machine housing, the said machine housing can be fitly inserted into the said insert slot to connect the said machine housing together with the said external housing body; 
a circuit board, the said circuit board is disposed on the inner side of the said machine housing at the position relative to the said insert slot; 
a connector, the said connector is disposed on one side of the said circuit board opposite to the said machine housing; 
an another connector, the said another connector is disposed inside the said insert slot at the position relative to the said connector and is connected with the circuit of the said display apparatus; 
wherein the said another connector and said connector contact with each other while the said machine housing being inserted into the said insert slot to connect the said machine housing together with the said external housing body.
